 the arguments on both sides. On the not-just-shareholders side, I like thi=
s 2019 memo from Marty Lipton et al.: =E2=80=9CTo be clear, Delaware law do=
es not enshrine a principle of shareholder primacy or preclude a board of d=
irectors from considering the interests of other stakeholders. Nor does the=
