_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-b=
ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;">that they</a> =E2=80=9Cmust benefit all of their =
stakeholders, including shareholders, employees, customers, and the communi=
ties in which they operate=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/27570320.267604/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxhY2tyb2NrLmNvbS91cy9pb=
